      "content": "hey so i had a small cyst removed by my doctor like 3 days ago here in sydney. the cut looks a bit red and feels kind of warm to the touch and there is a little bit of yellow stuff coming out of it. is that normal? can i just do a warm compress and put some neosporin on it to fix it up at home?",
