      "content": "it's not a lot of yellow stuff, just a tiny bit. i'm worried if i go back to the doctor they'll just charge me another huge fee for something that's probably nothing. if the redness isnt spreading fast, isn't a warm soak and some ointment usually enough to clear up a little bit of irritation like this?",
